QuestData.Title: Vol. X Pages ?
QuestData.Description:
The manual for the shredder was wedged in there, but it's missing lots of pages. We need to find as many pages of that manual as possible and I might--MIGHT--be able to get this shredder operational.
Based on the direction of the wind, I bet the pages flew toward Archenon Siegeyard.
QuestData.LogDescription: Find $1oa Manual Pages at Archenon Siegeyard.
QuestData.RewardText: Lots of detail... almost as if a goblin wrote it!
